msgid ""
"Output raster layer features of the point cloud layer are exported to. "
"Currently supported format is :file:`.TIF`."
msgstr ""
"Izlazni rasterski sloj u koji se izvoze objekti sloja oblaka tačaka. "
"Trenutno podržan format je :file:`.TIF`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/pointcloudconversion.rst:199
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``pdal:exportraster``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``pdal:exportraster``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/pointcloudconversion.rst:208
msgid "Export to raster (using triangulation)"
msgstr "Izvoz u raster (pomoću triangulacije)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/pointcloudconversion.rst:211
msgid ""
"Exports point cloud data to a 2D raster grid using a triangulation of points"
" and then interpolating cell values from triangles."
msgstr ""
"Izvozi podatke oblaka tačaka u 2D rastersku mrežu pomoću triangulacije "
"tačaka, a zatim interpolacijom vrednosti ćelija iz trouglova."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/pointcloudconversion.rst:214
msgid ""
"Using this algorithm can be slower if you are dealing with a large dataset. "
"If your point cloud is dense, you can export your ground points as a raster "
"using the :ref:`pdalexportraster` algorithm."
msgstr ""
"Korišćenje ovog algoritma može biti sporije ako radite sa velikim skupom "
"podataka. Ako je vaš oblak tačaka gust, tačke tla možete izvesti kao raster "
"pomoću algoritma :ref:`pdalexportraster`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/pointcloudconversion.rst:220
msgid "Terrain raster output generated by point cloud triangulation"
msgstr "Rasterski izlaz terena dobijen triangulacijom oblaka tačaka"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/pointcloudconversion.rst:318
msgid "**Exported (using triangulation)**"
msgstr "**Izvezeno (pomoću triangulacije)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/pointcloudconversion.rst:327
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``pdal:exportrastertin``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``pdal:exportrastertin``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/pointcloudconversion.rst:337
msgid "Export to vector"
msgstr "Izvoz u vektor"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/pointcloudconversion.rst:340
msgid ""
"Exports point cloud data to a vector layer with 3D points (a GeoPackage), "
"optionally with extra attributes."
msgstr ""
"Izvozi podatke oblaka tačaka u vektorski sloj sa 3D tačkama (GeoPackage), "
"opciono sa dodatnim atributima."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/pointcloudconversion.rst:346
msgid ""
"Exporting point cloud (ground points) to a vector layer styled based on the "
"elevation"
msgstr ""
"Izvoz oblaka tačaka (tačke tla) u vektorski sloj stilizovan na osnovu "
"nadmorske visine"

